FBIS3-10585 "drlat047_b_94007" FBIS-LAT-94-047 Document Type:Daily Report 10 Mar 1994 Antigua and Barbuda Haiti U.S. Official Pays Second Visit in 5 Days FL1003005894 Port-au-Prince Signal FM Radio in French 1130 GMT 9 Mar 94 FL1003005894 Port-au-Prince Signal FM Radio Language: French Article Type:BFN [Text] Michael Kozac, the assistant to the special representative of President Clinton in the Haitian crisis, arrived in Port-au-Prince on the afternoon of 8 March. During his stay, Mr. Kozac is to meet with Haitian businessmen and parliamentarians, such as members of the Senate office presided over by Firmin Jean-Louis. This is the second visit by Kozac in less than five days.
